# Local Claude Code Notes (template)

Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` (gitignored) and fill in machine-specific notes.
`CLAUDE.local.md` is automatically loaded by Claude Code sessions in this repo alongside
`CLAUDE.md`, so put host-specific paths, local service endpoints, routine IDs, or
credentials pointers here without leaking them into the shared repo doc.

## Local dev paths (example)

- Project checkout: `/absolute/path/here`
- Sibling repos (if relevant): infrastructure_scanner, infrastructure_portal at `/path/`
- Python venv: `.venv` at repo root (managed by `make install`)

## Claude Code routines (example)

| Routine | ID | Schedule | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| Doc drift check | `trig_...` | Daily | Flag drift between code and docs |
